Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.55,0:22:30.29,ed_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}君の名前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.29,0:22:33.83,ed_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}何があっても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.63,0:22:36.43,ed_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}必ず呼ぶから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.43,0:22:52.42,ed_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}君はぎざぎざハートの持ち主
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.90,0:22:57.84,ed_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}触れるものは何でも傷つけ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.14,0:23:03.10,ed_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}世界のすべてを睨みつけて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.10,0:23:05.86,ed_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}その目は言うんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.86,0:23:08.51,ed_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}僕はここにいる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.51,0:23:13.49,ed_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}誰かが笑ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.93,0:23:16.35,ed_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}だから引いたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.52,0:23:18.84,ed_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}その境界線
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.19,0:23:24.03,ed_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}それなら 私が
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.09,0:23:27.48,ed_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}その手を引く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.52,0:23:33.04,ed_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}連れてくから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.51,0:23:39.15,ed_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}言えないなら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.53,0:23:44.35,ed_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}この手を強く握って
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.73,0:23:46.31,ed_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}離さないで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.31,0:23:54.52,ed_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}君はもうひとりじゃないんだって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.44,0:23:57.40,ed_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\3c&HF6738D&\3a&H50}{\fad(200,200)}知ってほしんだよ
